  "texts": [
    "Our aim is not to exhaustively cover all text summarization models, datasets, and metrics but rather to focus on those utilized in the reviewed studies.",
    "Unlike extractive summarization, abstractive summarization approaches involve understanding the underlying semantics of the textual content and generating a new summary that is textually different from the original text.",
    "These approaches utilize complex neural network-based models that are black-box models due to their opacity and lack of interpretability.",
    "Therefore, explainability techniques are explored for abstractive summarization to ensure end-users understand and trust the summary generation process.",
    "This is evident in our results in Table 2, where explainability techniques are mostly applied to abstractive summarization."
  ],
